title: Put Together The Pieces
itunes:title: Put Together The Pieces
description:
Episode 519 - Steve Jobs said "You cannot connect the dots of your life looking forward, you can only connect them looking backwards." So when was the last time you looked into your past and noticed how everything that has happened to you has been perfectly designed for you to be where you are right now? Let's chat about that in this episode!
